{"tid":1366024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【救護】出到黎嘅基本急救知識","createTime":"2019-07-25T23:43:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T01:51:55.000Z","uid":275471,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1dc0e030cd4eabe86ae8972a13a318ef39345837","tid":1366024,"uid":275471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T23:43:47.000Z","msg":"首先呢我唔係在職醫護界從業員，個急救證書都就黎到期，只係以前有做過1年醫護行業<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最基礎嘅可以睇吓依遍野</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://telegra.ph/急救懶人包---目錄-07-21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2F%E6%80%A5%E6%95%91%E6%87%B6%E4%BA%BA%E5%8C%85---%E7%9B%AE%E9%8C%84-07-21&d=AixoiqhHuTrv0%2F0Xa%2FX9x5zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=e62e6423\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://telegra.ph/急救懶人包---目錄-07-21</a><br />\n唔算好複雜，有啲基礎嘅都識睇啦<br />\n<br />\n之後係搬運同包扎，依方面我強烈建議有考過試，pass埋先好幫人做<br />\n詳細嘅可以睇下&darr;<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DxRPP4ybSXo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDxRPP4ybSXo&d=AixoiqhHuTrv0%2F0Xa%2FX9x5zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=061f4abf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DxRPP4ybSXo</a><br />\n有意願做救護嘅手足就算係識，有時間嘅都可以再重溫下<br />\n<br />\n當然，臨時臨急都可以自己買哂教材同物資，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">搵個相熟又信得過嘅人</span></span>，同你一切自修<br />\n(最新AFA課程要8月報名，9月先有得入)<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記住</span></span><br />\n急救需要實踐，要自修架<br />\n至於急救教材同繃帶包可以喺&darr;<br />\n香港麥當勞道二號聖約翰大廔四樓救傷會接待處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.stjohn.org.hk/zh/shop\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stjohn.org.hk%2Fzh%2Fshop&d=AixoiqhHuTrv0%2F0Xa%2FX9x5zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=0701a06e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.stjohn.org.hk/zh/shop</a><br />\n買到<br />\n到時候我唔sure有幾多人需要急救，有能力嘅可以預個budget去買啲繃帶包，蒸餾水，生理鹽水，敷料，軟墊，哮喘藥，得力素，葡萄糖粉/碎<br />\n帶比物資組，或者直接拎去<span style=\"color: gold;\">臨時救護站</span>(唔確定有無)<br />\n<br />\n另外，想做救護嘅都係多多少少要有啲gear同心理準備，無唸住牛屎佬睇你救護就唔會打柒你<br />\n<br />\nThx to all 手足"},{"pid":"073c20b70f8bd5dbbc171ff45e21005f94529bed","tid":1366024,"uid":275471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T23:48:52.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292eb479222393afb7781f96fcfdedfff0b16f41","tid":1366024,"uid":275471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T23:50:34.000Z","msg":"繼續推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3194935bff32ac14c4b44106cbb87cbe1220d7c3","tid":1366024,"uid":175730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T23:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b47c36a644839afcff86fa019cce369574147cd","tid":1366024,"uid":275471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:32:24.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c84c48b4bae5a2aa571f3bce9977c5440f7bd6","tid":1366024,"uid":275471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:53:24.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"619517ed4a7ecf04072792490d0cf1ba2687d84a","tid":1366024,"uid":275471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:51:55.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}